data.description: Stop the car and come see this one first, move in ready! Located in central Chesapeake, it has easy access to downtown, interstate, bases and so much more! This beautiful home has 4 bedrooms and a bonus room, 2 full bathrooms & 1 half bathroom with a gorgeous front porch. Inside has an open concept, beautiful new floors & a lot of natural light. The kitchen is stunning with tall cabinets, granite countertops and all stainless steel appliances. Great for gatherings! The first floor primary bedroom gives you ease of access to living areas. 3 Large bedrooms are on the 2nd floor. The backyard is fully fenced with a privacy fence with a deck off the first floor and a balcony off the 2nd story. Very spacious yard for entertaining!
